One-party consent states (often cited): AL, AK, AZ, AR, CO, GA, HI (limited), ID, IN, IA, KS, KY, LA, ME, MN, MS, MO, NE, NJ, NM, NY, NC, ND, OH, OK, RI, SC, SD, TN, TX, UT, VA, WV, WI, WY

